OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry day with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells, though the odd shower is
OL,8,Fpossible. Moderate to fresh
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly dry this evening with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will be largely dry with
OL,14,Fclear periods and the odd passing
OL,15,Fshower. Fresh southwesterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FA dry day with with variable
OL,18,Famounts of cloud some sunny intervals.
OL,19,FFresh southwesterly winds across
OL,20,FShetland at first.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
