OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry on Monday, perhaps some low cloud
OL,7,Fand rain later. Generally dry although
OL,8,Fmostly cloudy on Tuesday and Wednesday.
